  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapo 3D is a classic 3D collect-a-thon platformer with linear levels, designed to be a short and fun experience with a gentle learning curve. Explore four different worlds while collecting golden flies to advance and face the final challenge, which lies behind the gigantic gate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/9ddb1a7ef232b3b86f62c9b5ddcfe6b9.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the little frog reach the end of the level and collect lots of golden flies. This way, he can open the portal to the next level, where he'll find more challenges and golden flies to catch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/d5849ab24cfdcda46bad98e05606b4c3.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1100 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/d5849ab24cfdcda46bad98e05606b4c3.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/d5849ab24cfdcda46bad98e05606b4c3.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/5390ca9fbd1629c516e5ea10a73aaa76.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face seed-spitting plants, explosive-egg-throwing chickens, giant-axe-wielding ladybugs, soda cannons, and even space missiles. Each world presents unique challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/698ce90f091ebd2e61c39c93753c2a20.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/698ce90f091ebd2e61c39c93753c2a20.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/698ce90f091ebd2e61c39c93753c2a20.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/beca9bd806af72e18a44b7116830caea.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The frog's control scheme is simple and easy to learn, but becomes more complex through interaction with powerups and objects in the environment. Use everything from jars that give you triple jumps to anti-gravity bubbles in space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/c2026b950b7403789e6bc5c0f2a0dd79.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/c2026b950b7403789e6bc5c0f2a0dd79.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/c2026b950b7403789e6bc5c0f2a0dd79.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/3cb4faf8ec425935a186230cbc12ba06.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open the giant gate in the main area when you've collected enough flies and discover its secret. Be prepared for the final challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/89cd712d18998286e68f5024e0f176ab.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1108 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/89cd712d18998286e68f5024e0f176ab.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/89cd712d18998286e68f5024e0f176ab.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And that's not all! After beating the game, you can also enjoy:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extra Stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A little secret for those who collect 100% of the flies in the game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/60ddaf36b2c79a68988b5914b69ce38b.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User interface and tutorials uses only symbols to convey information. So you can enjoy the game regardless of your native language!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/a98fb57f827be494258eee97d09120b4.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/a98fb57f827be494258eee97d09120b4.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/a98fb57f827be494258eee97d09120b4.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapo 3D is a classic 3D collect-a-thon platformer with linear levels, designed to be a short and fun experience with a gentle learning curve. Explore four different worlds while collecting golden flies to advance and face the final challenge, which lies behind the gigantic gate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/9ddb1a7ef232b3b86f62c9b5ddcfe6b9.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the little frog reach the end of the level and collect lots of golden flies. This way, he can open the portal to the next level, where he'll find more challenges and golden flies to catch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/d5849ab24cfdcda46bad98e05606b4c3.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1100 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/d5849ab24cfdcda46bad98e05606b4c3.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/d5849ab24cfdcda46bad98e05606b4c3.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/5390ca9fbd1629c516e5ea10a73aaa76.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face seed-spitting plants, explosive-egg-throwing chickens, giant-axe-wielding ladybugs, soda cannons, and even space missiles. Each world presents unique challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/698ce90f091ebd2e61c39c93753c2a20.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/698ce90f091ebd2e61c39c93753c2a20.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/698ce90f091ebd2e61c39c93753c2a20.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/beca9bd806af72e18a44b7116830caea.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The frog's control scheme is simple and easy to learn, but becomes more complex through interaction with powerups and objects in the environment. Use everything from jars that give you triple jumps to anti-gravity bubbles in space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/c2026b950b7403789e6bc5c0f2a0dd79.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/c2026b950b7403789e6bc5c0f2a0dd79.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/c2026b950b7403789e6bc5c0f2a0dd79.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/3cb4faf8ec425935a186230cbc12ba06.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open the giant gate in the main area when you've collected enough flies and discover its secret. Be prepared for the final challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/89cd712d18998286e68f5024e0f176ab.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1108 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/89cd712d18998286e68f5024e0f176ab.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/89cd712d18998286e68f5024e0f176ab.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And that's not all! After beating the game, you can also enjoy:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extra Stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A little secret for those who collect 100% of the flies in the game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/60ddaf36b2c79a68988b5914b69ce38b.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User interface and tutorials uses only symbols to convey information. So you can enjoy the game regardless of your native language!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/a98fb57f827be494258eee97d09120b4.poster.avif?t=1759255095\" width=1110 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/a98fb57f827be494258eee97d09120b4.webm?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963280/extras/a98fb57f827be494258eee97d09120b4.mp4?t=1759255095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
